<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <!-- Global Maven settings.xml. Shared by all projects at the build server. --> <settings xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/SETTINGS/1.0.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/SETTINGS/1.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/settings-1.0.0.xsd">
<interactiveMode>false</interactiveMode>
<mirrors> <mirror> <id>central</id> <url>${env.NEXUS_URL}/content/repositories/central</url> <mirrorOf>central</mirrorOf> </mirror> </mirrors>
</settings>
